# @sibis/valeiot-sdk

The `@sibis/valeiot-sdk` package provides a set of utilities and functions designed to streamline the development of IoT solutions with Valeiot.

## Installation

To use this package in your project, follow the steps below:

### Install the package:

```bash
npm install @sibis/valeiot-sdk
# or use your preferred package manager, like yarn or pnpm
```